high_descs: Turn around, move to the table on the right.
Pick up the red apple on the front of the table.
Turn left and bring the apple to the microwave next to the sink.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Take the heated apple out of the microwave, turn around, move to the table on the right.
Put the heated apple on the table, left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on the table, next to the potato.

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the leftmost apple that is on the white table.
Turn left and begin walking forward, then turn left again and walk over to the door, hang a right before you get there and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside to the left of the bowl, microwave the apple for a couple seconds, then remove it and close the microwave door.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn right again and walk up to the large white table on you right.
Place the heated apple on the large white table to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on a large white table.

pick up the apple directly below the bowl.
